main event: Multiple witnesses observed a low altitude object with flashing lights moving slowly from west to east, lasting for at least 15 minutes.
interesting points: Different witnesses reported the sighting at various times between 0300 and 0330, The object was described to have flashing lights, Witnesses did not report the sighting to any authorities, The object was suspended in the sky before moving rapidly away, The shape of the object was described as round and silvery with a bright glow.
witness description: An observer driving home from work who noticed the object in the sky.
